""
SELECT 
    p.nameFirst || ' ' || p.nameLast AS player_name, 
    MAX(b.G) AS games_played, 
    MAX(b.R) AS runs_scored, 
    MAX(b.H) AS hits, 
    MAX(b.HR) AS home_runs
FROM 
    player p 
JOIN 
    batting b ON p.playerID = b.playerID
GROUP BY 
    p.playerID
ORDER BY 
    games_played DESC, 
    runs_scored DESC, 
    hits DESC, 
    home_runs DESC
LIMIT 1
""
